Texts.Eng: Bring the ^orange;Atmosphere Regulator^reset; to ^green;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
Excellent, i'll use my 3d scanner to copy it. There we go. As promised, a ton of money.
I need an ^green;atmosphere regulator^reset; so I can colonize a hostile world. You'll find it at your ^orange;Power Station^reset;. I'll need to keep it for a while but I'll pay top dollar for it.
